{"tid":658272,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"比鬼壓","createTime":"2018-05-08T22:44:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T07:12:05.000Z","uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"455a89befe9104689d006986725737677bfc31bc","tid":658272,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:44:06.000Z","msg":"頭先日光日白，瞓喺有陽光到嘅睡房都奶嘢。<br />\n<br />\n鬼怕陽光的，所以呢個世界係無鬼、神，只係人腦咁啱腦分泌失調產生咗啲不適而已<br />\n<br />\n比鬼壓都所有肌肉都郁唔到，包括眼皮，只係呼吸可以繼續，因為呼吸由小腦控制。呼吸都要用到肌肉的。但心臟肌肉唔輪到意志去控制。"},{"pid":"706cf7822ec275851b44d9817a42d35785a40970","tid":658272,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:45:30.000Z","msg":"上次俾鬼壓完屎眼勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82ba3a90e074980eccc6f4c92013cf419ec19cd","tid":658272,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"706cf7822ec275851b44d9817a42d35785a40970","tid":658272,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:45:30.000Z","msg":"上次俾鬼壓完屎眼勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"844f4df082f83e2e6c50ba964877e2fcd77d7514","tid":658272,"uid":131245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"706cf7822ec275851b44d9817a42d35785a40970","tid":658272,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:45:30.000Z","msg":"上次俾鬼壓完屎眼勁痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T22:50:45.000Z","msg":"係咪你比人屌完記撚錯？"},{"pid":"55d90d98e34